# Implementation Note for External dependencies (ClShared)

Since the Collaborative Intelligence Blackboard lives in `/droid/repos/cl_shared`, it cannot be committed to this repository (`/mnt/droid/repos/c0rtana`). 

If the `cl_shared` repo is not already under version control by another process (or if I am expected to manage that too), I would need to switch contexts to perform those commits separately. For this cycle, I have successfully deployed the code to the environment.

Future cycles should verify who owns the commitment of the shared library files.
